snippet.title: Dr. Spacezoo - Steam Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Dr. Spacezoo - Steam Early Access Release Trailer

Rescue exotic space animals from a corrupt AI in Dr. Spacezoo, a chaotic twin-stick precision shoot-em-up for 1-4 players. Or reduce them to gibs. Your call, monster. 

Game: http://DrSpacezoo.com/
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/371380
Sound: https://soundcloud.com/smashriot/sets/dr-spacezoo
